<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Settings</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <h2>🤖 Refer & Earn Bot</h2>
            <div>
                <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/users">Users</a>
                <a href="/withdrawals">Withdrawals</a>
                <a href="/broadcast">Broadcast</a>
                <a href="/settings">Settings</a>
                <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
        
        <h1>⚙️ Bot Settings</h1>
        
        <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <form method="POST" action="/settings/update">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <label><strong>💰 Welcome Bonus (₹):</strong></label>
                    <input type="number" name="welcome_bonus" step="0.01" value="<%= welcomeBonus %>" required style="width: 200px; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">
                </div>
                
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <label><strong>👥 Refer Bonus (₹ per refer):</strong></label>
                    <input type="number" name="refer_bonus" step="0.01" value="<%= referBonus %>" required style="width: 200px; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">
                </div>
                
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <label><strong>💸 Minimum Withdrawal (₹):</strong></label>
                    <input type="number" name="min_withdraw" step="0.01" value="<%= minWithdraw %>" required style="width: 200px; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">
                </div>
                
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <label><strong>🎨 Welcome Message (Supports Markdown + Emojis):</strong></label>
                    <textarea name="welcome_message" rows="10" style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px;"><%= welcomeMessage %></textarea>
                    <div style="color: #666; margin-top: 5px; font-size: 14px;">
                        💡 <strong>Available placeholder:</strong> <code>{name}</code> - User's first name<br>
                        <strong>Markdown supported:</strong> *bold* _italic_ `code`<br>
                        <strong>Emojis:</strong> 🎉 🚀 💰 ✨ ✅ ⭐
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit">💾 Save Settings</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 30px; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <h3>📝 How to Use Welcome Message:</h3>
            <pre style="background: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto;">
Example with emojis:
🎉 *Swagat Hai {name}!* 🎉

💎 *Refer & Earn Bot* mein aapka swagat hai!

📌 *Pehle Ye Karo:*
⭐ Niche diye sare channels join karo
⭐ *₹5 instant* welcome bonus pao!

🚀 Refer karo aur unlimited earn karo!
            </pre>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
